<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Swisher International.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Swisher International.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said it initiated coverage of Swisher International Inc with a buy rating.</p>
<p>-- said the cigar company has strong brand franchise and demonstrated ability to create new brands.</p>
<p>-- expects earnings increasaes of of 93 percent to $0.87 a share in 1996, 27 percent to $1.10 a share in 1997, and 28 percent to $1.40 a share in 1998.</p>
<p>-- Swisher was off 1/4 to 15 in midday trading.</p>
<p>(( -- Wall Street Desk 212-859-1730))</p>
